<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天是星期五。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他非常期待周末。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>星期天，他要和爸爸一起去看足球比赛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我带了瓶子。” 他走进儿童中心说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31548</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们开始做糖和酵母气球吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道那是什么，但是听起来很酷！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“糖能给我们能量。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要给酵母一些糖。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“会发生什么呢？气球会膨胀吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师吹了吹气球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还是不会？” 她给气球放气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“酵母会让面包膨胀。” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以我觉得它会把气球吹起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“糖和酵母怎么会把气球吹起来呢？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83070</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他摇摇头。“我觉得不会。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们试试吧。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把一汤匙糖放进瓶子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我拿热水过来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比小心地把糖放进瓶子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上举起手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107828</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，我准备好了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师把温水倒进他的瓶子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在摇一摇！” 她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比用力摇了摇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，波比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>加酵母，把气球套在瓶口，然后轻轻摇一摇！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比把一袋酵母倒进瓶子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135293</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把蓝色气球套在瓶口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他又轻轻地摇了摇瓶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么都没发生。” 他抱怨道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要有耐心。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去外面边玩儿边等吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172137</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！” 大家一回来，莉琪就尖叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的气球变大了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家跑到莉琪的座位。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比跑到自己的座位。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的也变大了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太奇怪了。” 贾森看着气球说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195232</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么会变大？” 尼娜问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是谁把它吹大的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是糖和酵母。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>酵母其实是活着的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但它平时处在一个安静的睡眠状态。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当和水、糖混合时，它又活跃起来。” 雪莉老师解释说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226730</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当酵母吃了糖，它会产生气体，跑到气球里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有了气体，气球就被吹大了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230215</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就像我们吹气球时一样！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>理解了吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个高高的男人走进了体育馆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家在做什么？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“爸爸！快看！” 波比大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们把酵母、糖和水装在瓶子里混合起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>产生的气体把气球吹大了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263992</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听上去很有意思。” 波比的爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263992</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再过几个小时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265671</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们会看到酵母没有了糖会发生什么。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？还有事情会发生？” 波比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把气球带回家，我们在家里观察吧。” 他爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283201</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他可以和爸爸一起看足球和气球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个周末一定很棒！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>